extendedInfo.description: Enjoy the convenience, security and ease of doing your banking right from your mobile device. You can check your account balances, transfer funds, view recent activity, receive alerts, find ATMs or banking centers - even make check deposits from your phone.To get started, download and launch the app. Then sign on with your Sun Bank Online Banking Access ID and Password.
